<li>Thinking of you and your family during this difficult time.  May his memory be a blessing.</li>
<li>We are so sorry to hear about your loss.  Your father-in-law was a kind and wonderful man.</li>
<li>Words cannot express how sorry we are. Sending you strength and peace.</li>
<li>May the love you shared bring you comfort during this time of sorrow.</li>
